  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Mahanayake Theras have written an urgent letter to the President expressing their dissatisfaction with the current situation in the country",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mahanayake Theras have sent an urgent letter to the President asking him to speedily implement the 22nd Amendment Act and establish an honest all-party government.",
        "The chief prelates of four major Buddhist denominations in the country have written a 10-point petition to President Gotabhaya Rajapakse expressing their dissatisfaction with the current situation in the country.",
        "In the said letter, they urged immediate implementation of the 22nd Amendment to the Constitution to form an honest multi-party government.",
        "They accused the president of engaging in party politics at the moment and urged them to focus on finding appropriate solutions to the economic crisis.",
        "The Mahanayake Theras also point out that Sri Lanka has become a failed state as a result of an administration that acts without proper economic planning."
      ],
